A simple font viewer


BUILDING
========

Requires Gtk+, Cairo, Freetype2, HarfBuzz

To build:

$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install


To run:
 
$ fontview /path/to/a/typeface
 

To clean:

$ make clean

See COPYING for license information.
